      },
      "rationale": "Simulation setup independently reviewed by second CFD analyst using a 47-item checklist covering geometry import, boundary condition assignment, material property entry, turbulence model selection, and post-processing scripts. Three minor discrepancies identified and corrected before production runs. Final setup signed off by both analysts. Use error risk adequately mitigated at Gradation 2."
    },
