        "description": "Turbulence model selection (SST k-omega) justified by literature and pump-specific validation. Hemolysis power-law model applicability bounded by shear stress range in COU. Model form uncertainty estimated and included in total uncertainty budget."
      },
      "rationale": "SST k-omega selected based on published comparisons for rotating machinery at Re 1e5–1e6 (Ong et al. 2020, Hariharan et al. 2011). Model form uncertainty for turbulence estimated at ±9% NIH via comparison of SST, realizable k-epsilon, and RSM on validation dataset. Power-law hemolysis model valid for shear stress 50–600 Pa range; COU peak shear 380 Pa within bounds. Model form uncertainty included in total budget."
    },
