      "rationale": "Five independent experimental runs performed per operating point (n=5) using fresh bovine blood from separate donations. Hematocrit 33±2% verified by microhematocrit centrifuge before each run. Baseline plasma free hemoglobin < 5 mg/dL confirmed. Inter-replicate coefficient of variation 6.8% for NIH. Sample characterization fully documented per ASTM F1841. Satisfies Gradation 2."
